#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"New to the corp or to EVE? Our veterans will fly with you and show you the "
"ropes — from your first overview setup to your first fleet kill. Sign up as "
"a cadet, get paired with a mentor, and work through hands-on field exercises "
"at your own pace."
msgstr ""
"Nouveau dans la corpo ou sur EVE ? Nos vétérans voleront à tes côtés et te "
"montreront les ficelles — de ta première configuration d'overview à ton "
"premier kill en flotte. Inscris-toi comme cadet, sois jumelé à un mentor, et "
"avance à ton rythme à travers des exercices pratiques sur le terrain."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Welcome to the Corporation"
msgstr "Bienvenue dans la corporation"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "EVE Client & Overview Setup"
msgstr "Configuration du client EVE & de l'overview"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Travel, Safety & Survival"
msgstr "Voyage, sécurité & survie"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Ship Fitting & Doctrine Basics"
msgstr "Fitting de vaisseau & bases de doctrine"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "PvP Basics"
msgstr "Bases du PvP"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Fleet Operations"
msgstr "Opérations de flotte"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Logistics & Buyback Services"
msgstr "Logistique & services de buyback"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Manufacturing & Industry"
msgstr "Fabrication & industrie"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Skill Planning"
msgstr "Planification des compétences"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get plugged into comms, people and the way we do things."
msgstr "Branche-toi aux comms, aux gens et à notre façon de faire."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Make the client actually readable — overview, brackets, windows."
msgstr "Rends le client vraiment lisible — overview, brackets, fenêtres."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get where you're going and come back alive."
msgstr "Arrive à destination et reviens en vie."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Understand slots, tank, and why a doctrine fit is a doctrine fit."
msgstr ""
"Comprends les slots, le tank, et pourquoi un fit doctrine est un fit "
"doctrine."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Make ISK from rats without feeding your ship to a roam."
msgstr "Fais de l'ISK sur les rats sans offrir ton vaisseau à un roam."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Pull ore, compress it, and feed the buyback."
msgstr "Extrais du minerai, compresse-le, et alimente le buyback."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Scan it down, hack it, and get out clean."
msgstr "Scanne-le, hacke-le, et ressors proprement."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Tackle, hold point, follow the FC, and learn from the mail."
msgstr "Tackle, tiens le point, suis le FC, et apprends du mail."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Anchor, align, broadcast — be an asset in a fleet."
msgstr "Anchor, aligne-toi, broadcast — sois un atout en flotte."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Move things and turn loot into ISK, the corp way."
msgstr ""
"Transporte des marchandises et transforme le loot en ISK, à la manière de la "
"corpo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Blueprints, ME/TE, and installing your first job."
msgstr "Blueprints, ME/TE, et l'installation de ton premier job."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Train the right skills in the right order."
msgstr "Entraîne les bonnes compétences dans le bon ordre."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Read the corp rules & culture"
msgstr "Lis les règles & la culture de la corpo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Set up Discord / Mumble comms"
msgstr "Configure les comms Discord / Mumble"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn who the officers & FCs are"
msgstr "Apprends qui sont les officiers & les FCs"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Understand corp services (SRP, buyback, logistics, doctrines)"
msgstr ""
"Comprends les services de la corpo (SRP, buyback, logistique, doctrines)"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Link your character & grant baseline ESI"
msgstr "Lie ton personnage & accorde l'ESI de base"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Have your first onboarding chat with your mentor"
msgstr "Aie ta première discussion d'intégration avec ton mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Configure your overview"
msgstr "Configure ton overview"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Configure brackets & the tactical display"
msgstr "Configure les brackets & l'affichage tactique"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Lay out local, d-scan and the fleet window"
msgstr "Dispose le local, le d-scan et la fenêtre de flotte"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Mentor reviews your UI setup"
msgstr "Le mentor vérifie ta configuration d'UI"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn session-change timers & gate cloak"
msgstr "Apprends les timers de changement de session & le gate cloak"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to use directional scan"
msgstr "Apprends à utiliser le scan directionnel"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Create safe spots, tacticals & bookmarks"
msgstr "Crée des safe spots, des tacticals & des bookmarks"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Complete a travel exercise with your mentor"
msgstr "Réalise un exercice de voyage avec ton mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn high/mid/low/rig/drone/cargo slots"
msgstr "Apprends les slots high/mid/low/rig/drone/cargo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn CPU/PG, cap, resists, tank, range & application"
msgstr ""
"Apprends le CPU/PG, le cap, les resists, le tank, la portée & l'application"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review a corp doctrine fit with your mentor"
msgstr "Passe en revue un fit doctrine de la corpo avec ton mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Be able to fly a corp doctrine ship"
msgstr "Sois capable de piloter un vaisseau doctrine de la corpo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Create a skill plan toward a doctrine"
msgstr "Crée un plan de compétences vers une doctrine"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn safe ratting practice & aligning out"
msgstr "Apprends la pratique du ratting en sécurité & l'aligning out"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn site selection & when to dock up"
msgstr "Apprends la sélection des sites & quand te docker"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a ratting session with your mentor nearby"
msgstr "Fais une session de ratting avec ton mentor à proximité"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review a near-miss, loss or good tick"
msgstr "Analyse un quasi-accident, une perte ou un bon tick"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn mining ship roles & compression"
msgstr "Apprends les rôles des vaisseaux de minage & la compression"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the corp buyback flow"
msgstr "Apprends le flux de buyback de la corpo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Join a mining session"
msgstr "Rejoins une session de minage"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Submit a buyback lot"
msgstr "Soumets un lot de buyback"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn probe scanning"
msgstr "Apprends le scan aux sondes"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the hacking minigame"
msgstr "Apprends le mini-jeu de hacking"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn wormhole safety basics"
msgstr "Apprends les bases de la sécurité en wormhole"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Complete an exploration practice run"
msgstr "Réalise une sortie d'entraînement en exploration"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn tackle: scram, web, point, prop & transversal"
msgstr "Apprends le tackle : scram, web, point, prop & transversal"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to follow FC commands & broadcasts"
msgstr "Apprends à suivre les ordres & les broadcasts du FC"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Join a training roam or home-defence fleet"
msgstr "Rejoins un roam d'entraînement ou une flotte de home-defence"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review a killmail or lossmail with your mentor"
msgstr "Analyse un killmail ou un lossmail avec ton mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn fleet roles, anchoring & the watchlist"
msgstr "Apprends les rôles en flotte, l'anchoring & la watchlist"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Demonstrate correct broadcast usage"
msgstr "Démontre un usage correct des broadcasts"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Fly a real corp fleet op"
msgstr "Participe à une vraie opération de flotte de la corpo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Complete a mentor debrief after the op"
msgstr "Fais un débriefing avec ton mentor après l'opé"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn how to request freight & how courier contracts work"
msgstr ""
"Apprends à demander du freight & le fonctionnement des contrats de coursier"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the corp buyback rules"
msgstr "Apprends les règles de buyback de la corpo"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Complete a courier contract (or example)"
msgstr "Réalise un contrat de coursier (ou un exemple)"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Mentor confirms you understand the flow"
msgstr "Le mentor confirme que tu comprends le processus"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn blueprint basics (BPO vs BPC)"
msgstr "Apprends les bases des blueprints (BPO vs BPC)"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn material & time efficiency"
msgstr "Apprends l'efficacité de matériau & de temps"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Install a small industry job"
msgstr "Installe un petit job d'industrie"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review cost, materials & output with your mentor"
msgstr "Passe en revue le coût, les matériaux & le résultat avec ton mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review your current skills with your mentor"
msgstr "Passe en revue tes compétences actuelles avec ton mentor"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Choose a short-term training goal"
msgstr "Choisis un objectif d'entraînement à court terme"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Create a doctrine-relevant skill plan"
msgstr "Crée un plan de compétences pertinent pour une doctrine"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Re-check progress after a couple of weeks"
msgstr "Revérifie tes progrès après quelques semaines"

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Read the corp rules and code of conduct end to end."
msgstr "Lis les règles de la corpo et le code de conduite de bout en bout."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Install and log into the corp's comms tool and join the right channels."
msgstr ""
"Installe l'outil de comms de la corpo, connecte-toi et rejoins les bons "
"canaux."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn how to recognise officers, directors and fleet commanders."
msgstr ""
"Apprends à reconnaître les officiers, les directeurs et les fleet commanders."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Learn what SRP, buyback, freight and doctrines are and when to use them."
msgstr ""
"Apprends ce que sont le SRP, le buyback, le freight et les doctrines, et "
"quand les utiliser."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Link your main character so the tools can help you."
msgstr "Lie ton personnage principal pour que les outils puissent t'aider."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Sit down (on comms) with your mentor for a first proper chat."
msgstr ""
"Assieds-toi (sur comms) avec ton mentor pour une première vraie discussion."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Set up a clean overview with the right tabs and columns."
msgstr ""
"Configure un overview propre avec les bons onglets et les bonnes colonnes."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Tune brackets so grid is readable at a glance."
msgstr "Règle les brackets pour que la grid soit lisible en un coup d'œil."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Dock the local, directional-scan and fleet windows where you can see them."
msgstr ""
"Place les fenêtres du local, du scan directionnel et de la flotte là où tu "
"peux les voir."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Share your screen (or a screenshot) so your mentor can review your UI."
msgstr ""
"Partage ton écran (ou une capture d'écran) pour que ton mentor puisse "
"vérifier ton UI."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Understand session timers, gate cloak and the 'don't decloak into a camp' "
"rule."
msgstr ""
"Comprends les timers de session, le gate cloak et la règle « ne décloak "
"jamais dans un camp »."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to read d-scan — angle, range, and what a probe on scan means."
msgstr ""
"Apprends à lire le d-scan — angle, portée, et ce que signifie une sonde au "
"scan."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Make a few safes and tactical bookmarks in your home system."
msgstr "Crée quelques safes et bookmarks tactiques dans ton système d'origine."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Fly a short route with your mentor, using safes and d-scan the whole way."
msgstr ""
"Vole sur un court trajet avec ton mentor, en utilisant les safes et le d-"
"scan tout le long."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn what each slot type is for."
msgstr "Apprends à quoi sert chaque type de slot."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Understand the core fitting stats and the trade-offs between them."
msgstr ""
"Comprends les stats de fitting essentielles et les compromis entre elles."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Open a corp doctrine fit and go through every module with your mentor."
msgstr ""
"Ouvre un fit doctrine de la corpo et passe en revue chaque module avec ton "
"mentor."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Train into (or confirm you can already fly) at least one active doctrine "
"ship."
msgstr ""
"Entraîne-toi pour (ou confirme que tu peux déjà piloter) au moins un "
"vaisseau doctrine actif."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Use the skills tool to build a plan toward a doctrine hull."
msgstr ""
"Utilise l'outil de compétences pour construire un plan vers un hull doctrine."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to rat aligned, watch local/intel, and dock when it's spicy."
msgstr ""
"Apprends à ratter aligné, surveille le local/l'intel, et docke quand ça "
"chauffe."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn which sites to run and the triggers to stop."
msgstr "Apprends quels sites faire et les signaux qui disent d'arrêter."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a ratting session while your mentor is on comms / nearby."
msgstr ""
"Fais une session de ratting pendant que ton mentor est sur comms / à "
"proximité."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Talk through what happened on a run — good or bad."
msgstr "Discute de ce qui s'est passé pendant une sortie — en bien ou en mal."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the mining hull roles and why compression matters."
msgstr ""
"Apprends les rôles des hulls de minage et pourquoi la compression est "
"importante."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn how to turn ore into ISK via corp buyback."
msgstr "Apprends à transformer le minerai en ISK via le buyback de la corpo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Join a fleet mine (or mine near your mentor) and pull some ore."
msgstr ""
"Rejoins un minage en flotte (ou mine près de ton mentor) et extrais du "
"minerai."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Submit a real buyback lot for your ore."
msgstr "Soumettez un véritable lot buyback pour votre minerai."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to scan down cosmic signatures with probes."
msgstr "Apprenez à scanner les signatures cosmiques avec des sondes."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Practice the data/relic hacking minigame."
msgstr "Entraînez-vous au mini-jeu de hacking data/relic."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the rules for entering and leaving wormholes safely."
msgstr ""
"Apprenez les règles pour entrer et sortir des wormholes en toute sécurité."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Do a supervised exploration run and talk through each site."
msgstr ""
"Effectuez une sortie d'exploration supervisée et passez en revue chaque site."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn what scram/web/point do and how transversal keeps you alive."
msgstr ""
"Apprenez ce que font scram/web/point et comment la transversal vous garde en "
"vie."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the standard FC calls and how to use broadcasts."
msgstr "Apprenez les appels standard du FC et comment utiliser les broadcasts."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get on a killmail with the corp — a roam, gank or home defence."
msgstr ""
"Figurez sur un killmail avec la corpo — un roam, un gank ou une défense de "
"notre territoire."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Pull up a recent kill or loss and talk through what happened."
msgstr "Affichez un kill ou une perte récente et analysez ce qui s'est passé."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn wings/squads, anchoring, and what the watchlist is for."
msgstr "Apprenez les wings/squads, l'anchoring, et à quoi sert la watchlist."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Show you can broadcast for reps/target/align correctly."
msgstr "Montrez que vous savez broadcast correctement pour reps/target/align."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Sign up for and fly a corp operation."
msgstr "Inscrivez-vous à une opération de corpo et participez-y."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Debrief the op with your mentor afterwards."
msgstr "Débriefez l'op avec votre mentor ensuite."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn to book a courier and what collateral/reward mean."
msgstr ""
"Apprenez à créer un contrat courier et ce que signifient collateral/reward."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn what buyback pays and where."
msgstr "Apprenez ce que paie le buyback et où."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a real courier contract through the freight service."
msgstr "Réalisez un vrai contrat courier via le service de fret."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Talk your mentor through the whole logistics flow."
msgstr "Expliquez à votre mentor tout le processus logistique."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn the difference between BPOs and BPCs."
msgstr "Apprenez la différence entre les BPOs et les BPCs."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Learn what ME/TE do and why they matter."
msgstr "Apprenez ce que font le ME/TE et pourquoi c'est important."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Install a small manufacturing or research job."
msgstr "Lancez un petit job de fabrication ou de recherche."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Go over the BOM and margin of your job with your mentor."
msgstr "Passez en revue le BOM et la marge de votre job avec votre mentor."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Go through your current skills and gaps with your mentor."
msgstr "Passez en revue vos skills actuels et vos lacunes avec votre mentor."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Pick a concrete short-term skill goal."
msgstr "Fixez un objectif de skills concret à court terme."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Build a skill plan toward a corp doctrine."
msgstr "Élaborez un plan de skills vers une doctrine de corpo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Come back to your mentor after ~2 weeks to review progress."
msgstr "Revenez voir votre mentor après ~2 semaines pour faire le point."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Point your cadet at the rules doc; answer any questions."
msgstr ""
"Orientez votre cadet vers le doc des règles ; répondez à ses questions."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm your cadet can hear and be heard on comms."
msgstr "Vérifiez que votre cadet peut entendre et être entendu sur les comms."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Walk through the org chart and who to ask for what."
msgstr "Passez en revue l'organigramme et qui contacter pour quoi."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Give the tour of the corp's services and expectations."
msgstr "Présentez les services et les attentes de la corpo."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the cadet's character is linked and skills import."
msgstr ""
"Vérifiez que le personnage du cadet est lié et que les skills s'importent."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid ""
"Have a relaxed first session — goals, timezones, what they want from EVE."
msgstr ""
"Faites une première session détendue — objectifs, fuseaux horaires, ce "
"qu'ils attendent d'EVE."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review the cadet's overview live; fix obvious gaps."
msgstr ""
"Passez en revue l'overview du cadet en direct ; corrigez les lacunes "
"évidentes."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Sanity-check bracket settings."
msgstr "Vérifiez les réglages des brackets."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the window layout works."
msgstr "Vérifiez que la disposition des fenêtres fonctionne."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Do a full pass over the cadet's UI and overview."
msgstr "Faites une passe complète sur l'UI et l'overview du cadet."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain session timers and cloak with real examples."
msgstr "Expliquez les session timers et le cloak avec de vrais exemples."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a live d-scan drill with your cadet."
msgstr "Faites un exercice de d-scan en direct avec votre cadet."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Verify the cadet's safes are actually safe (off-grid)."
msgstr "Vérifiez que les safes du cadet sont vraiment sûrs (off-grid)."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Take the cadet on a supervised travel run through a chokepoint."
msgstr "Emmenez le cadet dans un trajet supervisé à travers un chokepoint."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Walk through slot layout on a real hull."
msgstr "Passez en revue la disposition des slots sur un vrai hull."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain the fitting stats with a doctrine fit open."
msgstr "Expliquez les stats de fitting avec un doctrine fit ouvert."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain why each module is on the doctrine fit."
msgstr "Expliquez pourquoi chaque module est sur le doctrine fit."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Help the cadet pick the fastest doctrine to get into."
msgstr "Aidez le cadet à choisir la doctrine la plus rapide à intégrer."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Help pick a sensible first doctrine skill goal."
msgstr "Aidez à choisir un premier objectif de skills de doctrine raisonnable."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain ratting safety and the 'align out' habit."
msgstr "Expliquez la sécurité en ratting et l'habitude de l'« align out »."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Cover site choice and bail triggers."
msgstr "Abordez le choix des sites et quand décrocher."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Watch intel and coach while your cadet rats."
msgstr "Surveillez l'intel et coachez pendant que votre cadet rat."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Debrief a real ratting moment with your cadet."
msgstr "Débriefez un vrai moment de ratting avec votre cadet."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain mining ships, boosts and compression."
msgstr "Expliquez les vaisseaux de minage, les boosts et la compression."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Walk through submitting a buyback lot."
msgstr "Montrez comment soumettre un lot buyback."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get the cadet into a mining op and confirm they mined."
msgstr "Emmenez le cadet dans une op de minage et confirmez qu'il a miné."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the cadet submitted a buyback lot."
msgstr "Confirmez que le cadet a soumis un lot buyback."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a scanning drill with your cadet."
msgstr "Faites un exercice de scan avec votre cadet."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Share hacking tips (node types, virus strength)."
msgstr "Partagez des astuces de hacking (types de nodes, virus strength)."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Cover WH mass/time and the 'bookmark both sides' rule."
msgstr "Abordez la mass/time des WH et la règle « bookmark des deux côtés »."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Take the cadet on a low-risk exploration run."
msgstr "Emmenez le cadet dans une sortie d'exploration à faible risque."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain tackle and range control with examples."
msgstr "Expliquez le tackle et le range control avec des exemples."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a quick comms/broadcast drill."
msgstr "Faites un exercice rapide de comms/broadcast."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Bring your cadet on a low-stakes fleet and get them on a mail."
msgstr ""
"Emmenez votre cadet sur une flotte à faible enjeu et faites-le figurer sur "
"un mail."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Debrief a real mail — what went right, what to change."
msgstr "Débriefez un vrai mail — ce qui a bien marché, ce qu'il faut changer."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain fleet structure and anchoring."
msgstr "Expliquez la structure de flotte et l'anchoring."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Check the cadet broadcasts the right things at the right time."
msgstr "Vérifiez que le cadet broadcast les bonnes choses au bon moment."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Get your cadet on a scheduled op and keep an eye on them."
msgstr "Emmenez votre cadet sur une op programmée et gardez un œil sur lui."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Run a short after-action with your cadet."
msgstr "Faites un court débrief après action avec votre cadet."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Walk through booking a freight contract."
msgstr "Montrez comment réserver un contrat de fret."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain the buyback rates and locations."
msgstr "Expliquez les tarifs et les emplacements du buyback."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the cadet completed (and ideally ESI-verified) a haul."
msgstr ""
"Confirmez que le cadet a réalisé (et idéalement vérifié via ESI) un haul."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the cadet understands collateral, reward and risk."
msgstr "Confirmez que le cadet comprend le collateral, le reward et le risque."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Explain blueprints and runs."
msgstr "Expliquez les blueprints et les runs."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Show ME/TE impact on a real build."
msgstr "Montrez l'impact du ME/TE sur un vrai build."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Help the cadet install their first job."
msgstr "Aidez le cadet à lancer son premier job."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review the economics of the cadet's job."
msgstr "Analysez la rentabilité du job du cadet."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Review the cadet's skills and obvious priorities."
msgstr "Passez en revue les skills du cadet et les priorités évidentes."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Help pick a motivating first goal."
msgstr "Aidez à choisir un premier objectif motivant."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Confirm the plan targets a doctrine the corp needs."
msgstr "Confirmez que le plan vise une doctrine dont la corpo a besoin."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "Follow up on the cadet's training progress."
msgstr "Suivez la progression de l'entraînement du cadet."

#: apps/mentorship/tracks_i18n.py
msgid "First Steps"
msgstr "Premiers pas"

