msgstr "(scope mail non accordé)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"In&#8209;game mail sends from this character. It must grant the mail-send "
"scope on the\n"
"      <a href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">ESI "
"scopes</a> page (feature: <span class=\"font-mono\">Pingboard mail sender</"
"span>)."
msgstr ""
"Les EVE-mails in&#8209;game partent depuis ce personnage. Il doit accorder "
"le scope d'envoi de mail sur la\n"
"      page <a href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan "
"hover:underline\">Scopes ESI</a> (fonctionnalité : <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">Pingboard mail sender</span>)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid "No Director characters are linked yet."
msgstr "Aucun personnage Directeur n'est encore lié."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"In&#8209;app alerts need no configuration — they appear in every targeted "
"pilot's Pingboard inbox automatically."
msgstr ""
"Les alertes in&#8209;app ne demandent aucune configuration — elles "
"apparaissent automatiquement dans la boîte de réception Pingboard de chaque "
"pilote ciblé."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid "How to get this value"
msgstr "Comment obtenir cette valeur"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Discord → <span class=\"text-ink\">Server Settings → Integrations → Webhooks "
"→ New Webhook</span>. Pick the target channel, <span class=\"text-ink\">Copy "
"Webhook URL</span>, and paste it above."
msgstr ""
"Discord → <span class=\"text-ink\">Paramètres du serveur → Intégrations → "
"Webhooks → Nouveau webhook</span>. Choisissez le canal cible, <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">copiez l'URL du webhook</span>, puis collez-la ci-dessus."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Easiest: create an <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming Webhook</span> at "
"api.slack.com/apps → your app → <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming Webhooks</"
"span>, and paste the <span class=\"font-mono\">hooks.slack.com/services/…</"
"span> URL. For DMs to pilots, set a bot token (<span class=\"font-"
"mono\">PINGBOARD_SLACK_BOT_TOKEN</span>) in the environment instead and give "
"a channel id."
msgstr ""
"Le plus simple : créez un <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming Webhook</span> "
"sur api.slack.com/apps → votre app → <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming "
"Webhooks</span>, puis collez l'URL <span class=\"font-mono\">hooks.slack.com/"
"services/…</span>. Pour les DM aux pilotes, définissez plutôt un token de "
"bot (<span class=\"font-mono\">PINGBOARD_SLACK_BOT_TOKEN</span>) dans "
"l'environnement et indiquez un id de canal."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Create a bot with <span class=\"font-mono\">@BotFather</span> → <span "
"class=\"font-mono\">/newbot</span> and copy its token into <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">Telegram bot token</span> above. Add the bot to your "
"group/channel, then read the chat id (e.g. via <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">@RawDataBot</span> or the Bot API <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">getUpdates</span>) and paste it. Everything is stored here — no "
"server access needed."
msgstr ""
"Créez un bot avec <span class=\"font-mono\">@BotFather</span> → <span "
"class=\"font-mono\">/newbot</span> et copiez son token dans <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">Token du bot Telegram</span> ci-dessus. Ajoutez le bot à "
"votre groupe/canal, puis relevez l'id de chat (par ex. via <span "
"class=\"font-mono\">@RawDataBot</span> ou l'API Bot <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">getUpdates</span>) et collez-le. Tout est stocké ici — aucun accès "
"serveur requis."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Pick <span class=\"text-ink\">Meta Cloud API</span> or <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">Twilio</span> and paste that provider's credentials from its console — "
"access/auth token above, ids/numbers in the fields. All stored here, "
"encrypted; no server access needed. Note: outside a 24&#8209;hour "
"user&#8209;initiated window both backends require a pre&#8209;approved "
"message template."
msgstr ""
"Choisissez <span class=\"text-ink\">Meta Cloud API</span> ou <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">Twilio</span> et collez les identifiants de ce "
"fournisseur depuis sa console — token d'accès/d'authentification ci-dessus, "
"ids/numéros dans les champs. Tout est stocké ici, chiffré ; aucun accès "
"serveur requis. Note : en dehors d'une fenêtre de 24&#8209;heures initiée "
"par l'utilisateur, les deux backends exigent un modèle de message "
"pré&#8209;approuvé."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Any linked Director character can send. Have them open the ESI scopes page "
"and grant <span class=\"text-ink\">Pingboard mail sender</span>, then select "
"them above."
msgstr ""
"N'importe quel personnage Directeur lié peut envoyer. Demandez-lui d'ouvrir "
"la page Scopes ESI et d'accorder <span class=\"text-ink\">Pingboard mail "
"sender</span>, puis sélectionnez-le ci-dessus."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
