"grant — the pilot must connect their token first. The app never moves ISK; "
"tickets are recorded, prizes delivered by hand."
msgstr ""
"Les attributions ne fonctionnent que pour les <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">pilotes inscrits disposant d'un token ESI valide</span>. Si le "
