"Rules whose channels include <span class=\"text-ink\">EVE-mail</span> send "
"in-game from this director to the responsible officer, for <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">high</span>/<span class=\"text-ink\">critical</span> "
"alerts. The chosen director must grant the <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">Readiness mail sender</span> scope on the <a href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" "
"class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">ESI scopes</a> page — until then EVE-"
"mail degrades to a no-op."
msgstr ""
"Les règles dont les canaux incluent <span class=\"text-ink\">EVE-mail</span> "
"envoient en jeu, depuis ce directeur vers l'officier responsable, pour les "
"alertes <span class=\"text-ink\">élevées</span>/<span class=\"text-"
"ink\">critiques</span>. Le directeur choisi doit accorder le scope <span "
"class=\"font-mono\">Readiness mail sender</span> sur la page <a "
"href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">Scopes ESI</a> — "
"jusque-là, l'EVE-mail reste sans effet."

