#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/support.html
msgid ""
"The skills that make a fleet survivable and boosted — warfare-link\n"
"    specialists, command bursts, logi cap-transfer, and the like. The <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">Fleet Support</span>\n"
"    dimension scores the share of members trained to each one (at the level "
"you set), averaged across the list.\n"
"    <span class=\"text-ink\">While this list is empty the dimension is "
"unavailable</span> — it stays disabled until you add a skill."
msgstr ""
"Les compétences qui rendent une flotte résistante et boostée — spécialistes "
"des warfare links,\n"
"    command bursts, transfert de cap en logi, et ainsi de suite. La "
"dimension <span class=\"text-cyan\">Soutien de flotte</span>\n"
"    évalue la part des membres entraînés à chacune d'elles (au niveau que "
"vous fixez), moyennée sur la liste.\n"
"    <span class=\"text-ink\">Tant que cette liste est vide, la dimension est "
"indisponible</span> — elle reste désactivée jusqu'à ce que vous ajoutiez une "
"compétence."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/support.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The Fleet Support dimension is <span class=\"text-cyan\">enabled</span> and "
"contributes to the readiness index. Adjust this on <a href=\"%(url)s\" "
"class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; weights</a>."
msgstr ""
"La dimension Soutien de flotte est <span class=\"text-cyan\">activée</span> "
"et contribue à l'indice de préparation. Ajustez cela sur <a href=\"%(url)s\" "
"class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; pondérations</a>."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/support.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This dimension scores now but is <span class=\"text-ink\">not yet in the "
"index</span> — enable it on <a href=\"%(url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; weights</a> when you're ready."
msgstr ""
"Cette dimension est évaluée mais <span class=\"text-ink\">pas encore comptée "
"dans l'indice</span> — activez-la sur <a href=\"%(url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; pondérations</a> quand vous serez prêt."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/support.html
msgid "Support skills"
msgstr "Compétences de soutien"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/support.html
msgid ""
