#: templates/admin_audit/console/relay_settings.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"No corp character currently holds the notifications or mail scope. A "
"director needs to grant <code class=\"text-faint\">esi-"
"characters.read_notifications.v1</code> / <code class=\"text-faint\">esi-"
"mail.read_mail.v1</code> on the <a href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan "
"hover:underline\">ESI scopes page</a> first."
msgstr ""
"Aucun personnage de la corp ne détient actuellement le scope notifications "
"ou mail. Un directeur doit d'abord accorder <code class=\"text-faint\">esi-"
"characters.read_notifications.v1</code> / <code class=\"text-faint\">esi-"
"mail.read_mail.v1</code> sur la <a href=\"%(scopes_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan "
"hover:underline\">page ESI Scopes</a>."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid ""
"How long each class of data is kept before the nightly\n"
"    housekeeping job prunes it, and what happens to a member's data when "
"they leave. These drive the\n"
"    daily retention task."
msgstr ""
"Combien de temps chaque classe de données est conservée avant que la tâche "
"de maintenance nocturne ne la purge, et ce qu'il advient des données d'un "
"membre lorsqu'il part. Ces réglages pilotent la tâche de rétention "
"quotidienne."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "Pruned nightly."
msgstr "Purgé chaque nuit."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "Stored — enforcement not yet wired."
msgstr "Enregistré — application pas encore branchée."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "Keep for (days)"
msgstr "Conserver (jours)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "On member leave"
msgstr "Au départ d'un membre"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "Enforced"
msgstr "Appliqué"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid ""
"“On member leave” is applied by the daily sweep below to each class\n"
"      set to <span class=\"text-ink\">Delete</span> (Retain and Anonymise "
"keep the data — these per-character\n"
"      classes have no faithful anonymised form, so Anonymise is treated as "
"Retain for now)."
msgstr ""
"« Au départ d'un membre » est appliqué par le balayage quotidien ci-dessous "
"à chaque classe réglée sur <span class=\"text-ink\">Supprimer</span> "
"(Conserver et Anonymiser gardent les données — ces classes par personnage "
"n'ont pas de forme anonymisée fidèle, Anonymiser est donc traité comme "
"Conserver pour l'instant)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "On-member-leave enforcement"
msgstr "Application au départ d'un membre"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid ""
"A daily sweep applies the “on member leave” policy above to the data of "
"pilots\n"
"      whose whole account has left the corp. It is <span class=\"text-"
"loss\">destructive</span>, so it runs in\n"
"      <span class=\"text-ink\">report-only</span> mode until you arm it — "
"review the projected impact below first."
msgstr ""
"Un balayage quotidien applique la politique « au départ d'un membre » ci-"
"dessus aux données des pilotes dont le compte entier a quitté la corp. Il "
"est <span class=\"text-loss\">destructif</span> : il s'exécute donc en mode "
"<span class=\"text-ink\">rapport seul</span> tant que vous ne l'avez pas "
"armé — examinez d'abord l'impact projeté ci-dessous."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "Arm enforcement (actually delete departed members' data)"
msgstr ""
"Armer l'application (supprimer réellement les données des membres partis)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "Last sweep"
msgstr "Dernier balayage"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "report-only"
msgstr "rapport seul"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid "enforced"
msgstr "appliqué"

